{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — app EMBED. This is the ENGINE: it loads the storefront controller site-wide
  (every page, so it reacts to the cart drawer opening from anywhere) and renders a hidden config
  element the controller reads.

  Enable it in the theme editor under: Theme settings (gear) -> App embeds -> "Free Gift Engine".

  Phase 5b-2b-1: the perception UI (tier progress graph + OR/variant chooser + decline) is mounted by
  JS as an OVERLAY on <body>, positioned over the cart drawer and shown/hidden with it — so it sits
  ABOVE the backdrop (clickable) and SURVIVES the drawer's inner re-render on every cart change. No
  static mount node is needed (the old [data-fge-chooser] band that sat at the bottom of the page is
  gone). Choices come from the shopper's selection (the `default_choices` seam was retired in 5b-2a).

  PORTABILITY: the controller auto-detects the cart drawer (e.g. Dawn's <cart-drawer>, open class
  `active`). If a production theme differs, override without code via the optional attributes below:
    data-drawer-selector="<css selector for the drawer element>"
    data-drawer-open-class="<class the theme toggles when the drawer opens>"
{% endcomment %}

<div
  data-fge-app-block
  data-proxy-path="/apps/free-gift/validate"
  data-presentment-currency="{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}"
  data-country="{{ localization.country.iso_code }}"
  hidden
></div>

<script src="{{ 'free-gift.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift Engine",
  "target": "body",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
